    "body": "Problem:\r\nbuild.zig always downloads dependencies and statically links them, which is frowned upon by distro packagers.\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\nAdd option to use system libraries.\r\n\r\nIn this initial PR I've done this for libuv, libluv, utf8proc, unibilium, and tree-sitter.\r\nI believe the others need closer inspection/input from the maintainers.\r\n",
